{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"dcf736093e","title":"祝贺中国、中央两航空公司全体员工起义的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"66e324cfac","index":0,"year":1949,"month":11,"day":12,"articleId":"dcf736093e"}],"tags":[{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"da76decafe","type":"title","text":"祝贺中国、中央两航空公司全体员工起义的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"dcf736093e"},{"id":"e771d5b868","type":"paragraph","text":"中国航空公司刘敬宜总经理，中央航空公司陈卓林总经理，及两公司全体员工同志们：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"dcf736093e"},{"id":"34c8d486fd","type":"paragraph","text":"中国航空公司和中央航空公司全体员工在两公司总经理领导下，毅然脱离国民党反动残余，投入人民祖国怀抱，这是一个有重大意义的爱国举动。特向你们表示祝贺、欢迎和感问。希望你们团结一致，为建设人民航空事业，并为保卫留在香港的祖国财产而奋斗。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"dcf736093e"},{"id":"9c94ef4522","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"dcf736093e"},{"id":"9f5a1da74c","type":"paragraph","text":"一九四九年十一月十二日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"dcf736093e"},{"id":"cefb35635b","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]中国航空公司和中央航空公司是原国民党政府的两个民用航空公司。1948年年底，这两个公司将营业机航基地从上海分别迁移到香港和广州。1949年11月9日，中国航空公司总经理刘敬宜、中央航空公司总经理陈卓林乘机由香港飞抵北京，发布全体员工起义通电，同时飞回大陆的还有11架飞机。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"dcf736093e"}],"page":{"id":"55f6eb5224","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"dcf736093e","start":511,"end":511}}}},"__N_SSG":true}